1
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:24,980
THE GOOD BAD MOTHER

2
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:28,150
-You punk.
-What the…

3
00:00:28,230 --> 00:00:30,860
-You punk. How could you do that?
-What's wrong with you?

4
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:32,400
-How could you?
-What's with you?

5
00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:33,900
-Calm down.
-I mean,

6
00:00:33,990 --> 00:00:36,030
of all people,

7
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:38,870
how could you do that to Kang-ho,

8
00:00:38,950 --> 00:00:39,990
that poor kid?

9
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:42,120
Why do you pity him?

10
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:44,290
-What?
-He got all the attention

11
00:00:44,370 --> 00:00:46,960
for being smart and getting good grades.

12
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:49,670
And now he's getting all the attention
because he's become an idiot.

13
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:52,090
As if his mom's love isn't enough,

14
00:00:52,170 --> 00:00:55,300
even the lady next door dotes on him.

15
00:00:55,840 --> 00:01:00,140
You were always too busy with the mill
to make me a birthday meal,

16
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:01,760
but when Kang-ho got into SNU,

17
00:01:01,850 --> 00:01:05,310
you even closed the mill
and threw him a feast!

18
00:01:05,390 --> 00:01:07,190
Darn it, I'm your kid, not him.

19
00:01:07,270 --> 00:01:09,480
Why do you think I did that?

20
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,360
I thought you'd benefit a little

21
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:15,990
if you were around a smart kid like him.

22
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:18,700
It was humiliating and frustrating,

23
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:21,660
but I still put up with everything.

24
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:23,740
That's…

25
00:01:24,370 --> 00:01:26,620
That's how I held out.

26
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:33,340
Why are you crying?
You're breaking my heart. It's all right.

27
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:38,510
Hey, you punk.
Why are you making my woman cry?

28
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:41,390
I needed some money.

29
00:01:41,970 --> 00:01:43,430
I wanted to work,

30
00:01:43,510 --> 00:01:46,350
but I couldn't get a job anywhere
with my criminal record.

31
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:49,020
How much do you need?

32
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:50,480
Tell me!

33
00:01:54,690 --> 00:01:57,280
-Two…
-What? Two million won?!

34
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,280
Two million won?!

35
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,950
You cursed punk! Two million won?!

36
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:08,750
Look who it is.

37
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:09,960
My love Mi-joo…

38
00:02:12,250 --> 00:02:14,460
Mom, where are we going?

39
00:02:16,210 --> 00:02:18,420
Where is she going this early?

40
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:27,100
Hello?

41
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:30,100
What?

42
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:31,140
Kang-ho.

43
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:35,060
Let's eat and get ready.

44
00:02:36,650 --> 00:02:38,740
We'll be having a guest soon.

45
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,320
You're upsetting me right now.

46
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,160
Mom, where are we going?

47
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:58,840
This is Kang-ho oppa's place.

48
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,260
Ye-jin.

49
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,810
Seo-jin.

50
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,710
Mom?

51
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:40,130
Mom!

52
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,380
Mom?

53
00:03:43,970 --> 00:03:45,050
Mom.

54
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,720
Mom!

55
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,760
Mom!

56
00:03:54,060 --> 00:03:56,100
Excuse me.

57
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:58,730
Is this Mr. Choi Kang-ho's place?

58
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,440
Yes.

59
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:01,650
This is it.

60
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,820
Don't give out
his personal information to a stranger!

61
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:09,200
Who are you
and why are you looking for him?

62
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:12,120
My name is Hoang.

63
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:14,250
I'm supposed to meet him today,

64
00:04:14,330 --> 00:04:16,330
but I couldn't get in touch.

65
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:19,790
Mom.

66
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,920
Mi-joo, my mom…

67
00:04:24,010 --> 00:04:25,880
-What?
-Mom…

68
00:04:25,970 --> 00:04:26,970
What's going on?

69
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:29,260
Mom.

70
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:32,810
Ms. Jin!

71
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:34,430
-Mom, please.
-Ms. Jin, wake up.

72
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,020
-Mom.
-Ms. Jin!

73
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,560
-Oh, no.
-No…

74
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:39,900
-Don't shake her like that. Please move.
-Sorry?

75
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:41,020
Okay.

76
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,620
She's in hypovolemic shock.

77
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:54,790
Hello? I'm calling from Jou-ri.

78
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,250
We have a medical emergency.

79
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:59,130
Kang-ho, bring me a thick blanket
and pillows.

80
00:04:59,210 --> 00:05:00,960
Okay, a blanket and pillows.

81
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,880
-A blanket…
-How long will it take?

82
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,760
It's an emergency.

83
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,260
Please come quickly.

84
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:08,800
-Yes.
-Lift up her legs so the blood

85
00:05:08,890 --> 00:05:10,470
-can get to her heart.
-Legs.

86
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,970
-Higher.
-Higher.

87
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:15,180
-Okay.
-You two go wait at home.

88
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:17,390
Is Ms. Jin dead?

89
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,650
No. Don't worry.

90
00:05:20,150 --> 00:05:22,110
Seo-jin, go home with Ye-jin.

91
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,150
Okay?

92
00:05:23,650 --> 00:05:25,740
Good. Get home safely.

93
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,450
Ms. Hoang.

94
00:05:28,530 --> 00:05:31,490
-Can you stay with her for 20 minutes?
-Yes, of course.

95
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,580
Kang-ho, where's the car key?

96
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:35,580
The car key?

97
00:05:36,450 --> 00:05:38,830
HAPPY FARM

98
00:05:45,090 --> 00:05:47,170
License plate 6169, pink truck.

99
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:50,090
Pull over to the right. You're speeding.

100
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:52,890
License plate 6169, pull over!

101
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,140
-Pull up next to them.
-Yes, sir.

102
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,270
What are you doing?

103
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:02,770
-Pull over.
-Can't you hear me?

104
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:04,230
You're speeding!

105
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:06,320
Sir! Please help us!

106
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,610
-What?
-My mom just collapsed.

107
00:06:08,690 --> 00:06:09,820
It's hy…

108
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:11,070
Hy…

109
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,740
Hypovolemic shock.

110
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,490
Hypovolemic… What?

111
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:16,040
-Hypovolemic shock.
-Hype?

112
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,500
What are you saying?

113
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:19,500
Hypovolemic shock!

114
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:22,040
-What?
-She's in hypovolemic shock!

115
00:06:22,130 --> 00:06:23,500
-Hurry up and go.
-Yes, sir.

116
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:26,170
We're escorting an emergency patient.

117
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:28,170
Please make way.

118
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:34,140
-Put her on IV.
-What's wrong with my mom?

119
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:35,470
Why is she ill?

120
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,770
I'm sorry, but please wait outside.

121
00:06:37,850 --> 00:06:39,390
No, I want to stay here.

122
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,350
Let's wait outside

123
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,980
so that she can get treated.

124
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:51,860
Thank you.

125
00:06:52,490 --> 00:06:54,030
We arrived safely

126
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,450
thanks to your first aid.

127
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:57,790
I should thank you.

128
00:06:58,410 --> 00:07:01,790
You drove her here
without waiting for the ambulance,

129
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:05,750
so my mother-in-law
could get treated quickly.

130
00:07:06,670 --> 00:07:07,840
I see.

131
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,670
-Hey.
-Here.

132
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:13,930
You must be in shock.

133
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:18,470
We're at the hospital now,
so you can relax.

134
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,600
Thank you.

135
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,810
By the way, who are you?

136
00:07:26,690 --> 00:07:30,650
I didn't get to introduce myself
in the midst of this chaos.

137
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:36,280
My name is Hoang,
and we were supposed to meet today.

138
00:07:39,490 --> 00:07:40,950
Ms. Jin Young-soon's guardian?

139
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,250
-Yes?
-Yes?

140
00:07:43,210 --> 00:07:45,710
You wanted to open
a clothing store, didn't you?

141
00:07:46,210 --> 00:07:47,840
I'll open one for you,

142
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:51,010
but make a small space in a corner
for a nail salon.

143
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:52,800
It's not for you!

144
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:54,380
It's for Mi-joo!

145
00:07:54,470 --> 00:07:57,260
I'll sell my garlic field
and whatever else to fund it,

146
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:01,180
so take Mi-joo and the twins
and look after them.

147
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,310
Your sister

148
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:05,230
will be ruined if she stays here.

149
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,810
Goodness.

150
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:13,610
Goodness, it smells rotten.

151
00:08:14,450 --> 00:08:16,660
It smells like an old man.

152
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,030
Hoon-ah?

153
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:21,870
Are you here?

154
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:25,920
My goodness, this place reeks.

155
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,050
What's all this?

156
00:08:37,090 --> 00:08:38,390
Baek Hoon-ah!

157
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:41,430
Goodness! What the hell are you doing?

158
00:08:42,010 --> 00:08:43,470
Serves you right.

159
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:45,270
You're getting punished.

160
00:08:45,890 --> 00:08:48,060
Right, that pig lady.

161
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:50,020
How's she doing these days?

162
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:52,940
The foot-and-mouth disease
took a toll on her,

163
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,780
but she's doing better now.

164
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:56,150
Not that.

165
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,570
Then what? Her son?

166
00:08:57,660 --> 00:09:00,200
That woman.

167
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,160
Good grief, how frustrating!

168
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,330
What?

169
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:04,910
She hasn't told anybody?

170
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,870
She's still keeping it a secret?

171
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:09,000
What are you talking about?

172
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,380
A secret?

173
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:14,510
She's critically ill?

174
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:17,090
She has stage four stomach cancer.

175
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:20,760
The cancer cells have metastasized
to her peritoneum and lungs,

176
00:09:20,850 --> 00:09:21,970
so there's…

177
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,930
Excuse me.

178
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:27,730
I'm sorry, Doctor,

179
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:29,650
but please speak with me.

180
00:09:30,770 --> 00:09:35,030
It's tough for him to understand
what you're saying right now.

181
00:09:35,990 --> 00:09:39,410
I'm a friend of his and--

182
00:09:39,490 --> 00:09:40,910
No.

183
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:44,160
Please speak with me. I want to hear it.

184
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,120
I'm…

185
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:48,660
I'm my mom's guardian.

186
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:56,550
Kang-ho, wait.

187
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,760
Kang-ho!

188
00:10:12,810 --> 00:10:14,070
Mom, get up.

189
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:17,990
Mom, get up. Come with me.

190
00:10:18,570 --> 00:10:20,360
Mom, let's go home.

191
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:22,280
Kang-ho, don't do this.

192
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:25,490
Come home with me, Mom.

193
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:27,500
Mom, open your eyes!

194
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:32,790
Mom…

195
00:10:36,090 --> 00:10:38,170
Mom, I'm sorry.

196
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:41,220
I'll do as you say from now on.

197
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:42,390
I won't…

198
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:44,140
I won't be a prosecutor anymore.

199
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,600
Mom, please get up.

200
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,020
-Kang-ho, stop it.
-Mom.

201
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:51,440
Mom, I won't like Mi-joo anymore,
just as you wanted.

202
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:54,520
I won't like Mi-joo anymore.

203
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:57,270
Mom, so please, wake up.

204
00:10:59,610 --> 00:11:01,950
Wake up, Mom.

205
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,500
Hey, Andrea.

206
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,210
I think

207
00:11:13,290 --> 00:11:16,290
you set me up with the wrong guy.

208
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,340
Is anybody…

209
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:25,220
up there?

210
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,600
Is anyone…

211
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:31,810
really up there?

212
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:36,520
I know you can be cruel,

213
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,610
but this is way too harsh.

214
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,650
Wasn't it enough

215
00:11:43,860 --> 00:11:44,950
to take her husband

216
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:48,530
and make her son like that?

217
00:11:50,450 --> 00:11:54,120
What did that good woman ever do?

218
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:55,750
Goodness.

219
00:11:57,330 --> 00:11:59,460
How could you try to take her life too?

220
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:01,760
Grandma!

221
00:12:06,090 --> 00:12:08,050
Grandma, where have you been?

222
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:10,810
We looked everywhere for you.

223
00:12:10,890 --> 00:12:13,770
Ms. Jin collapsed!

224
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:15,020
She collapsed?

225
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:16,020
When?

226
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:16,980
This morning.

227
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:20,980
Mom and Kang-ho oppa
took her to the hospital.

228
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:27,240
YOUNGEST DAUGHTER MI-JOO

229
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,370
Gimbap with no carrots.

230
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:33,580
Eat some.

231
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:38,750
Everyone Mom made gimbap for

232
00:12:40,130 --> 00:12:41,960
never returned home.

233
00:12:44,090 --> 00:12:45,970
Grandma, Grandpa,

234
00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:48,510
and Dad too.

235
00:12:50,350 --> 00:12:52,600
That's why she never let me go
on a school picnic.

236
00:12:54,310 --> 00:12:55,850
She was afraid I wouldn't return.

237
00:13:00,110 --> 00:13:02,940
So my mom isn't a bad person.

238
00:13:03,530 --> 00:13:04,610
You're right.

239
00:13:05,740 --> 00:13:07,530
She's not a bad person.

240
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,490
Then why is she ill?

241
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:17,670
I'm getting punished
because I'm a bad person.

242
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:21,250
But why is my mom being punished?

243
00:13:23,590 --> 00:13:24,960
No, Kang-ho.

244
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:28,010
Neither of you

245
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:31,100
is getting punished.

246
00:13:32,810 --> 00:13:33,720
This is…

247
00:13:35,930 --> 00:13:37,810
something that nobody wants,

248
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:41,440
but something that can happen to anybody.

249
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,190
Just as Ms. Jin was there for you

250
00:13:46,190 --> 00:13:48,400
when you were unwell,

251
00:13:49,410 --> 00:13:50,490
it's your turn

252
00:13:51,070 --> 00:13:52,990
to stay strong by her side.

253
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,160
Okay?

254
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,170
She's going to be fine.

255
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:12,050
She'll be okay.

256
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:13,050
Hey!

257
00:14:13,850 --> 00:14:15,390
Hey, get away from him!

258
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:19,060
What are you two doing in broad daylight?

259
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:20,190
Mom.

260
00:14:20,850 --> 00:14:21,770
Hello.

261
00:14:21,850 --> 00:14:23,690
I'm afraid I don't have time
to exchange greetings.

262
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:26,110
Where's your mom?

263
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,860
I'll stay here.

264
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:34,450
You should go home
and look after your kids.

265
00:14:34,530 --> 00:14:35,660
Listen, Mom.

266
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:41,120
Go home.

267
00:14:41,210 --> 00:14:43,210
You darn brat.

268
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:45,130
You crazy bitch.

269
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,670
I ought to…

270
00:14:49,090 --> 00:14:50,170
Lead the way.

271
00:14:59,180 --> 00:15:00,940
Ma'am, what are you doing?

272
00:15:01,730 --> 00:15:03,770
You can't do this.

273
00:15:04,940 --> 00:15:06,980
Let go of me!

274
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,610
Doctor.

275
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:12,400
Will I live if I get this IV shot?

276
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,990
Will I live if I stay in bed?

277
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,740
If not, let me go.

278
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:19,660
Help me make the best use

279
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:23,120
