01:05:10,900 --> 01:05:12,190
That's because…

1112
01:05:13,070 --> 01:05:14,280
But you know,

1113
01:05:15,280 --> 01:05:17,700
I don't miss him that much either.

1114
01:05:18,320 --> 01:05:19,240
What?

1115
01:05:19,330 --> 01:05:21,620
Maybe it's because
we've been apart for so long.

1116
01:05:22,450 --> 01:05:25,500
He feels like a stranger.

1117
01:05:26,170 --> 01:05:27,960
I don't feel attached to him.

1118
01:05:29,290 --> 01:05:31,250
So I wanted you to know that

1119
01:05:32,050 --> 01:05:35,510
you don't have to put up with him
because of us.

1120
01:05:36,220 --> 01:05:37,680
Just get a divorce.

1121
01:05:39,140 --> 01:05:41,180
Being divorced is not a big deal nowadays.

1122
01:05:41,890 --> 01:05:44,350
There are three divorced families

1123
01:05:45,310 --> 01:05:46,480
in my kindergarten.

1124
01:05:47,060 --> 01:05:49,900
At first, they threw a fit
and even refused to eat,

1125
01:05:49,980 --> 01:05:53,150
but now they run about happier than ever.

1126
01:05:53,230 --> 01:05:55,110
It's such a mess.

1127
01:05:56,740 --> 01:05:58,030
So,

1128
01:05:59,620 --> 01:06:02,200
stop worrying about us

1129
01:06:02,910 --> 01:06:04,790
and start living your own life.

1130
01:06:07,670 --> 01:06:10,000
If there's one thing
I learned in all my years,

1131
01:06:10,540 --> 01:06:12,670
it's that there isn't much to life.

1132
01:06:13,250 --> 01:06:15,420
You just have to live happily

1133
01:06:16,220 --> 01:06:18,720
with the people you love, right?

1134
01:06:19,800 --> 01:06:21,850
You love us.

1135
01:06:22,850 --> 01:06:24,930
And we love you too.

1136
01:06:26,060 --> 01:06:27,310
So please,

1137
01:06:28,350 --> 01:06:31,560
let's just live happily by ourselves.

1138
01:06:32,520 --> 01:06:35,690
I'll marry Kang-ho oppa in the future

1139
01:06:36,490 --> 01:06:38,320
and take good care of you.

1140
01:06:44,240 --> 01:06:45,660
Come here, my baby.

1141
01:06:45,750 --> 01:06:47,580
Goodness, come here.

1142
01:06:50,120 --> 01:06:51,500
You little thing.

1143
01:06:52,170 --> 01:06:54,300
You must've been worried sick.

1144
01:06:54,380 --> 01:06:57,130
It must've been so hard for you.

1145
01:06:58,590 --> 01:06:59,880
I'm sorry.

1146
01:07:01,390 --> 01:07:02,640
I'm…

1147
01:07:03,470 --> 01:07:05,260
such a bad mom.

1148
01:07:06,640 --> 01:07:09,190
I'm such a bad mom.

1149
01:07:11,310 --> 01:07:12,440
You're crying again.

1150
01:07:12,520 --> 01:07:13,810
-What?
-You haven't smiled once

1151
01:07:13,900 --> 01:07:16,190
since you've come back here.

1152
01:07:17,400 --> 01:07:20,650
I want to see you smile.

1153
01:07:21,700 --> 01:07:24,410
Because you're not a bad mom,

1154
01:07:24,490 --> 01:07:26,290
but a pretty mom.

1155
01:07:44,510 --> 01:07:45,640
Hello?

1156
01:07:47,600 --> 01:07:48,600
What?

1157
01:07:50,640 --> 01:07:52,520
There's smoke coming from the farm?

1158
01:07:53,230 --> 01:07:54,810
Yes, okay.

1159
01:07:55,690 --> 01:07:57,070
Yes, I'll check now.

1160
01:08:01,530 --> 01:08:02,660
Kang-ho.

1161
01:08:03,610 --> 01:08:04,870
Kang-ho, wake up.

1162
01:08:04,950 --> 01:08:06,580
There's smoke coming from the farm.

1163
01:08:19,300 --> 01:08:20,380
Mom.

1164
01:08:20,920 --> 01:08:22,220
Oh, no!

1165
01:08:23,510 --> 01:08:25,640
-Mom.
-Our pigs!

1166
01:08:26,180 --> 01:08:27,930
Guys, wake up!

1167
01:08:29,010 --> 01:08:30,270
We need to leave.

1168
01:08:30,350 --> 01:08:31,980
-We have to get out.
-No.

1169
01:08:32,060 --> 01:08:33,310
We have to get out!

1170
01:08:34,690 --> 01:08:36,560
-Mom, no.
-Our pigs.

1171
01:08:36,650 --> 01:08:37,980
-Mom, we have to go!
-Let go!

1172
01:08:38,070 --> 01:08:39,320
-We have to go!
-Let go!

1173
01:08:39,980 --> 01:08:42,700
-No!
-We have to go now!

1174
01:08:43,400 --> 01:08:45,200
No!

1175
01:08:56,130 --> 01:08:57,040
Mom.

1176
01:09:01,920 --> 01:09:03,170
-No!
-It won't open.

1177
01:09:03,260 --> 01:09:04,340
Why won't it open?

1178
01:09:21,320 --> 01:09:22,360
Mom.

1179
01:09:22,860 --> 01:09:25,490
Mom, come here. This way.

1180
01:09:25,570 --> 01:09:28,030
Mom, we have to get out of here.

1181
01:09:28,620 --> 01:09:30,580
-Mom, get out of here. Now.
-No.

1182
01:09:30,660 --> 01:09:32,620
-Mom, we have to leave now!
-No.

1183
01:09:33,290 --> 01:09:34,210
Come on.

1184
01:09:34,290 --> 01:09:35,210
Mom!

1185
01:09:35,920 --> 01:09:37,920
Kang-ho, you go first.

1186
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:39,500
-You go…
-No, Mom.

1187
01:09:39,590 --> 01:09:42,380
You have to get out first. Mom!

1188
01:09:43,260 --> 01:09:46,800
You have to leave first.
I'll follow you out, okay?

1189
01:09:46,880 --> 01:09:48,050
Come on.

1190
01:09:48,140 --> 01:09:50,140
Hurry.

1191
01:09:51,350 --> 01:09:52,430
Mom.

1192
01:09:55,730 --> 01:09:56,770
Mom.

1193
01:10:25,840 --> 01:10:28,180
Yong-yong, have you been well?

1194
01:10:29,800 --> 01:10:30,760
Yong-yong.

1195
01:10:31,300 --> 01:10:32,640
Do you copy, Yong-yong?

1196
01:10:32,720 --> 01:10:34,270
Do you remember Daddy's voice?

1197
01:10:35,390 --> 01:10:36,810
What are you up to?

1198
01:10:37,560 --> 01:10:38,690
Are you still asleep?

1199
01:10:39,600 --> 01:10:41,270
It's time to get up.

1200
01:10:41,810 --> 01:10:43,360
Wake up and play with me.

1201
01:10:44,020 --> 01:10:45,650
My dear son,

1202
01:10:46,190 --> 01:10:48,700
it's time to wake up.

1203
01:11:08,760 --> 01:11:11,680
THE GOOD BAD MOTHER

1204
01:11:31,740 --> 01:11:32,910
Fire!

1205
01:11:32,990 --> 01:11:35,990
Are you saying Kang-ho is in there?

1206
01:11:36,080 --> 01:11:39,580
Was it you? Were you the girl
he wrote about in his journal?

1207
01:11:40,620 --> 01:11:43,290
Sam-sik, you know something, don't you?

1208
01:11:43,380 --> 01:11:45,000
I really need to see Ha-young.

1209
01:11:45,090 --> 01:11:47,420
Did you have that much fun with her?

1210
01:11:49,090 --> 01:11:53,260
Mr. Choi, you're under arrest on suspicion
of murdering Ms. Hwang Soo-hyun.

1211
01:11:54,640 --> 01:11:56,060
I'm going to protect Kang-ho.

1212
01:11:56,850 --> 01:12:00,350
Kang-ho was only able to endure
those lonely and painful years

1213
01:12:00,850 --> 01:12:02,020
because of you.

1214
01:12:02,100 --> 01:12:03,850
Do you think she's really here?

1215
01:12:03,940 --> 01:12:06,270
She has to be. For Kang-ho's sake.

1216
01:12:07,570 --> 01:12:12,570
Subtitle translation by: Eun-sook Yoon